# Risk Management Document

## Identified Risks

| Risk | Probability | Impact | Mitigation Strategy |
|------|-------------|--------|---------------------|
| Team member unavailable | Medium | High | Distribute tasks evenly and have backup plans |
| Technical issues with Trello | Low | Medium | Use alternative tracking methods like Excel |
| Missing deadline | Low | High | Set early reminders and weekly check-ins |
| Poor communication | Medium | Medium | Schedule regular group meetings on Telegram |
| GitHub learning curve | Medium | Low | Watch tutorial videos and practice |

## Risk Response Plan

### High Priority Risks
- **Team member unavailable**: Each task should have a secondary responsible person

### Medium Priority Risks
- **Poor communication**: Daily updates via group chat

### Low Priority Risks
- **Technical issues**: Have backup documentation ready

